    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">The Impact of E-Waste</h2>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="text-success mb-3">
              <i class="fas fa-globe-americas fa-2x"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="h5">Environmental Impact</h3>
            <p>E-waste contains toxic substances like lead, mercury, and cadmium that can contaminate soil, water, and air when improperly disposed of.</p>
            <p>Improper e-waste disposal contributes to pollution, habitat destruction, and climate change.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
