            </div>
            <h3 class="h5">Health Impact</h3>
            <p>Exposure to e-waste toxins can cause respiratory problems, neurological damage, and increased risk of cancer.</p>
            <p>Workers in informal e-waste recycling operations are particularly vulnerable to health risks from improper handling.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
