            </div>
            <h3 class="h5">Economic Impact</h3>
            <p>Discarded electronics represent a significant loss of valuable resources and rare earth elements.</p>
            <p>Proper e-waste recycling creates jobs, recovers valuable materials, and reduces the need for raw material extraction.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
